778&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f64f79821872e1bf19b3d363851cb192&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/o02wSnKAPeHagVMGJkofckGrZE1RlB12zvPHYcY0qQQN7ias9whcu55gsjJJXF4dOibG3xxnU7s9QfZEoTDnONn8meAmRhbrFXu1r0ITlp7WM/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"8\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23333333333333334\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/o02wSnKAPeHagVMGJkofckGrZE1RlB12zvPHYcY0qQQN7ias9whcu55gsjJJXF4dOibG3xxnU7s9QfZEoTDnONn8meAmRhbrFXu1r0ITlp7WM/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"135\" data-imgfileid=\"101396704\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=034d95a8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fo02wSnKAPeHagVMGJkofckGrZE1RlB12zvPHYcY0qQQN7ias9whcu55gsjJJXF4dOibG3xxnU7s9QfZEoTDnONn8meAmRhbrFXu1r0ITlp7WM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></a></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4166666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: 241px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"241\" data-imgfileid=\"101298602\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=87b607f5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0LereibpbkBWeO9ZkPaT3HA1GmlmABENQmcfuVicLhA8MJnBVLEPpRmwlY5n0HA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2828507795100223\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"898\" style=\"height: 163px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"163\" data-imgfileid=\"101298601\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cedb1d4d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0Lereibph6S4cD1udwTvHO1f1TGc38MPePRKKvibuBqd6BCmY7buGgDxiaoUxgWA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.14444444444444443\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: 84px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"81\" data-imgfileid=\"101298603\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=419a6fb5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0LereibpVtBKUEjKhlcnTamERSCcPu00rbtswUB7cpAibmAe1GzGWa8vDh5zvRw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"%27%27\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=367c256e&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzI2NDk5NzA0Mw%3D%3D%26mid%3D2248880524%26idx%3D2%26sn%3D3938cb620cebd3c31ee21292e7db40a6\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深度剖析了老铺黄金在金价上涨背景下，通过大幅调价反而引发抢购的“奢侈品化”商业逻辑及其面临的竞争挑战。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深度剖析了老铺黄金在金价上涨背景下，通过大幅调价反而引发抢购的“奢侈品化”商业逻辑及其面临的竞争挑战。",
  "summary": "文章聚焦 2026 年初老铺黄金创纪录的 20%-30% 调价现象。在行业集体涨价的背景下，老铺黄金凭借脱离传统“克重+工费”的“一口价”模式，成功构建了基于古法工艺与品牌稀缺性的奢侈品定价体系。这种策略不仅未劝退消费者，反而强化了“越涨越买”的投资预期。文章进一步探讨了老铺在二级市场表现出的高保值率与流通性，将其定义为“可穿戴资产”。然而，随着国际金价持续走高对毛利率的挤压，以及周大福、君佩等竞争对手在古法金赛道的发力，老铺黄金的品牌护城河正面临考验。",
  "mainPoints": [
